{{> header}}
<h1>New sign-in to your account</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}}, we noticed a new sign-in to your Team Workspace account from a device we haven't seen before.</p>
<div class="card">
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
  <p><strong>IP address:</strong> {{ip}}</p>
  <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{userAgent}}</p>
</div>
<p>If this was you, no action is needed.</p>
<hr>
<div class="alert">
  <p>⚠️ &nbsp;<strong>Wasn't you?</strong> Your account may be at risk. <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color:#92400e;font-weight:600;">Change your password immediately</a> and contact support.</p>
</div>
{{> footer}}
